OL,3,CIan Paterson gives inquest evidence
OL,4,Cfor first time into death of former
OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FJailed breast surgeon Ian Paterson has
OL,8,Fstarted giving evidence in court for
OL,9,Fthe first time today, at an inquest
OL,10,Finto the death of one of his former
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,FElaine Turbill who was 63 and from
OL,14,FSolihull, was diagnosed with breast
OL,15,Fcancer and had a mastectomy carried
OL,16,Fout by Paterson. She died in 2017.
