OL,7,FPaterson has been giving evidence from
OL,8,Fprison via videolink where he is
OL,9,Fcurrently serving a 20-year sentence
OL,10,Ffor wounding patients in the private
OL,11,Fsector.
OL,13,FHe had previously refused to take part
OL,14,Fin the inquests of 62 patients.
OL,16,F"No breast surgeon aims to leave
OL,17,Fbreast tissue after breast surgery,
OL,18,Fthat's just crazy"
