OL,7,FBirmingham and Solihull Coroner's
OL,8,FCourt has been hearing more background
OL,9,Ffrom Paterson about his history as a
OL,10,Fsurgeon.
OL,12,FHe told the inquest about a "cleavage-
OL,13,Fsparing mastectomy", and the court has
OL,14,Fbeen hearing discussion about the
OL,15,Fdifference between breast tissue and
OL,16,Fbreast fat.
