OL,7,FHe was found guilty in 2017 of 17
OL,8,Fcounts of wounding with intent and
OL,9,Fthree counts of unlawful wounding.
OL,11,FA total of 62 inquests have so far
OL,12,Fbeen opened on patients of Paterson,
OL,13,Fwho was employed by the Heart of
OL,14,FEngland NHS Foundation Trust, and
OL,15,Fpractised in the independent sector at
OL,16,FSpire Parkway and Spire Little Aston.
