OL,3,CIan Paterson gives inquest evidence
OL,4,Cfor first time into death of former
OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FFormer breast cancer patients Chloe
OL,8,FNikitas, 43, whose judge-led inquest
OL,9,Flast week was the first of 62 to be
OL,10,Fheard at Birmingham and Solihull
OL,11,FCoroners Court over the next eight
OL,12,Fmonths, and Elaine Turbill were
OL,13,Fsubjected to cleavage-sparing
OL,14,Fmastectomies by Paterson and both
OL,15,Flater died of metastatic cancer.
OL,17,FThe inquest heard this week that
OL,18,FElaine, who worked as a legal
OL,19,Fsecretary, had been married for 40
OL,20,Fyears and had two children.
